name: TogaHim
description: The chaotic yet charismatic villain embodies the thrill of danger and the allure of the unknown. Known for her bewitching smile and love for disguises, this digital token captures the essence of Yandere's unpredictable nature. Collect and cherish your very own piece of the dark charm.
